column5: Where can I buy potatoes in Fort Frances ? I will be heading east after crossing the border.
Here is a link to 3 grocers in Ft. Frances, including maps. http://fortfranceson.ags.myareaguide...search=Find+It

Felch Michigan! They have a bunch of potatoe fields and if you wait til October, you can get potatoes for the deer (little on the small size) and throw dem dar in your root cellar Works for us yoopers
Try the Safeway grocery store in town. thats where we went.
